<h2>Instant<br/>Demos and Skins</h2>
 <h3>Just install the free WooCommerce plugin and the Shoppe theme, then click demo import—within a minute, you will get an exact shop site like our demo. Shoppe theme offers additional theme skins that transform your site with a complete different look &#038; feel. Select a skin and click import demo, your site will be setup instantly like our demo.</h3>
 
 <a href="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe-black/" > <img src="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2017/01/shoppe-black-skin-360x230.jpg" width="360" height="230" title="Black" alt="Black" /> </a> <h3> <a href="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe-black/" > Black </a> </h3> 
 
 <a href="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe-elegant/" > <img src="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2017/01/elegant-360x230.jpg" width="360" height="230" title="Elegant" alt="Elegant" /> </a> <h3> <a href="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe-elegant/" > Elegant </a> </h3> 
 
 <img src="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2017/01/more-to-come-shoppe-360x230.jpg" width="360" height="230" title="More to come" alt="More to come" srcset="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2017/01/more-to-come-shoppe.jpg 360w, https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2017/01/more-to-come-shoppe-300x192.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px" /> <h3> More to come </h3> 
<h2>Drag & drop<br/>Builder Layout</h2>
 <h3>Using Themify Builder, you can build almost design any layout as you can imagine and it is responsive. If time is a concern, simply import a pre-designed layout included in the theme. There are over 60+ regular layouts and 20+ shop landing page layouts.</h3>
 
 <img src="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2016/12/shoppe-layouts-1200x517-1400x603.jpg" width="1400" height="603" alt="shoppe layouts" srcset="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2016/12/shoppe-layouts.jpg 1400w, https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2016/12/shoppe-layouts-300x129.jpg 300w, https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2016/12/shoppe-layouts-768x331.jpg 768w, https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2016/12/shoppe-layouts-1200x517.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px" /> 
<h2>Smart &<br/>Flexible Layouts</h2>
 <h3>Shoppe theme includes tons of layout options. The layout resource files (CSS and Javascript) are smarly loaded when the layout is selected, making the theme load fast without having to load all unnecessary files. It is so flexible that you can select the layout either for the entire site or per page basis (ie. you can have a different layout on different pages if you wish).</h3>
 <h4>14 Header Layouts</h4><h5>Over 14 header layout options are available—whether you like it minimal, tall, skinny, big, left, right, fullwidth, boxed, you got it!</h5>
 
 <a href="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/features/header-layouts/" > <img src="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2016/12/header-layouts-1158x576.jpg" width="1158" height="576" alt="header layouts image" srcset="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2016/12/header-layouts.jpg 1158w, https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2016/12/header-layouts-300x149.jpg 300w, https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2016/12/header-layouts-768x382.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1158px) 100vw, 1158px" /> </a> 
 <h4>9 Archive Layouts</h4><h5>For post archive layouts, there are traditional list-post, 4-column, 3-column, 2-column, tiles, and slider with additional options like masonry, overlay, and polaroid style.</h5>
 
 <a href="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/all-archives-layouts/" > <img src="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2016/12/archive-icon-1157x389.jpg" width="1157" height="389" alt="archive icon" srcset="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2016/12/archive-icon.jpg 1157w, https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2016/12/archive-icon-300x101.jpg 300w, https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2016/12/archive-icon-768x258.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1157px) 100vw, 1157px" /> </a> 
 <h4>6 Footer Layouts</h4><h5>The footer offers various layouts like block style, left and right column styles.</h5>
 
 <a href="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/features/footer-layouts" > <img src="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2016/12/footer-layouts-1158x203.jpg" width="1158" height="203" alt="footer layouts image" srcset="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2016/12/footer-layouts.jpg 1158w, https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2016/12/footer-layouts-300x53.jpg 300w, https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2016/12/footer-layouts-768x135.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1158px) 100vw, 1158px" /> </a> 
<h2>UX Enhancements<br/>Details & Features</h2>
 <h3>Building an ecommerce site has never been so easy with Shoppe theme. Impress visitors with these shop features—they will sure make your shop like a big brand.</h3>
 
 <img src="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2017/01/ajax-cart.gif" title="Ajax Cart" alt="When users adds an item to cart, it instantly updates the dropdown cart on the header without reloading the page. Users can view the cart total and as well remove items on the ajax cart." /> <h3> Ajax Cart </h3> When users adds an item to cart, it instantly updates the dropdown cart on the header without reloading the page. Users can view the cart total and as well remove items on the ajax cart. 
 
 
 <img src="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2017/01/wishlist-animation.gif" title="Wishlist" alt="Wishlist feature allows users to add their favorite items which can revisit later. When an item is wishlisted, there is a sparkling animation to enhance user experience." /> <h3> Wishlist </h3> Wishlist feature allows users to add their favorite items which can revisit later. When an item is wishlisted, there is a sparkling animation to enhance user experience. 
 
 <img src="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2016/12/quicklook.gif" title="Quick Look" alt="Quick look allows users to view the details of an item in a lightbox without going to the product page. A nifty flipping animation will show when the quick look lightbox is loading." /> <h3> Quick Look </h3> Quick look allows users to view the details of an item in a lightbox without going to the product page. A nifty flipping animation will show when the quick look lightbox is loading. 
 
 <img src="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2017/01/gallery-slider-animation.gif" title="Gallery Slider" alt="On archive porduct, when the product image is hovered, an ajax product gallery slider will appear allowing the user to see all product images." /> <h3> Gallery Slider </h3> On archive porduct, when the product image is hovered, an ajax product gallery slider will appear allowing the user to see all product images. 
 
 <img src="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2016/12/image-zoom.gif" title="Image Zoom" alt="Image zoom allows users to click to view the large version of the product image. It works on desktop, tablet, and mobile." /> <h3> Image Zoom </h3> Image zoom allows users to click to view the large version of the product image. It works on desktop, tablet, and mobile. 
 
 <img src="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2017/01/share-animation.gif" title="Product Share" alt="A convenient share button is placed next to the buy button. Having an easy-to-access share button increases sharing rate." /> <h3> Product Share </h3> A convenient share button is placed next to the buy button. Having an easy-to-access share button increases sharing rate. 
 
 <img src="https://themify.me/demo/themes/shoppe/files/2017/01/ajax-search.gif" title="Ajax Search" alt="One of the powerful features in Shoppe theme is the ajax search function. It allows users to quickly search anything on your site and filter the search results between the blog posts and products." /> <h3> Ajax Search </h3> One of the powerful features in Shoppe theme is the ajax search function. It allows users to quickly search anything on your site and filter the search results between the blog posts and products. 
 
